\": 763, \"to\": 779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not say, 'You are keeping us all together, we are relying on you and you alone',\\\" Memmel told journalists days before the Games begin in the French capital.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5062509355764778, \"rank\": 0.7911097087303676, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 822}, {\"ngram\": \"Memmel\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"journalists\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles' coach Cecile Landi approached coaching staff to discuss expectations on the four-time Olympic champion, who disclosed her mental health struggles during the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles' coach\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"Cecile Landi\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"coaching staff\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"expectations\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"the four-time Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health struggles\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If she does not feel like it's going to be in her best interest to do all four events that day, is that an option for her?\\\"\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her best interest\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"all four events\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"an option\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Memmel said Landi asked.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Memmel\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"Landi\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And we said: absolutely.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If that's what she needs to continue to be at her best for her team and for herself, then that's what we are going to do because there are still four other members on our team.\\\"\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her team\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"four other members\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"our team\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, 27, returns to the glare of the Olympic spotlight in women's qualifying on July 28 with the team final on July 30, three years after struggling with the disorienting mental block that gymnasts call the \\\"twisties\\\".\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"the glare\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spotlight\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"women's qualifying\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1569}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"the disorienting mental block\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"twisties\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles dazzled at the 2016 Rio Games, winning gold in all-around, vault, floor exercise and team events.\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Rio Games\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"all-around\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"vault\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"floor exercise\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"team events\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She arrived at the pandemic-delayed Tokyo Games with superstar billing and history in her sights.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pandemic-delayed Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"superstar billing\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"her sights\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She withdrew from the majority of her events but came back to win team silver and bronze on the balance beam.\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"her events\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"team silver\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"the balance beam\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Memmel said that the team did not want Biles to feel she was the glue holding them together.\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Memmel\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"the glue\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, I think for her, just knowing that she has that option... now whether she takes it or not, it's going to be completely up to her.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that option\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We also talked about that with her at worlds last year, and she ultimately decided